<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Sociology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5946</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">SOS 131</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Introduction to Social Science</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">7</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">09.11.2021</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">First, students are going to read texts deconstructing the concept of “science”. Then, the believed-to- be features of natural sciences will be questioned and the problem of objectivity will be discussed. The course will also explore similarities and differences between natural sciences.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=131969&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
