<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">27.02.2021</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Introduction of Anthropology and social anthropology
Research methods of social anthropology
Culture
Forms of livelihood
Economic systems
Social structures and functions
Kinship systems
Marriage and family institutions
Socialization
Ethnicity and social stratification
Power and politics
Normative order
Religion</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=131854&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
