</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Sociology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5946</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 153</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">How to Read a Photo?</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">12.01.2021</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The content of the course will begin with a conceptual understanding of Photography, Photography with all its dimensions; taking, taking and looking at the photo, opening up a discussion, explaining what it says and how it says. The course will be supported by photographs taken by recognized photographers outside of the source texts or photographs taken in our daily lives, which will provide an understanding of visual culture and language.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=131834&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Sociology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5946</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 154</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Cultural Memory: How We Remember, Why We Forget</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">12.01.2021</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The relationship that societies establish with the past in order to create themselves becomes more and more obvious every day. In this course the topics such as introduction to cultural memory, your memory remembering and forgetting the history of the relationship between the processes of how and what we remember with effects (visual, narrative), related to the cultural memory of popular culture, nostalgia, memories of the reality will be explained and discussed over important texts.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=131835&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Sociology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5946</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 155</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Time and Stress Management</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">29.03.2021</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Time and stress management means planning our time in a way that can combine our goals, responsibilities, tastes and activities contained in our social life.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=131995&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Sociology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5946</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 156</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Sports For All</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">29.03.2021</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">In all segments of society, old, young, children, women, men, healthy, disabled, fit, fit people in existing natural conditions or in areas created later, for health with or without tools, or for the positive assessment of leisure time, providing physiological and psychological benefits to gain scientific competence that can make sports.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=131993&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
