<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">By evaluating the phenomenon of language with its various dimensions such as language-thought, language-individual, Language-Society, language-culture, each student will be able to comprehend how important language really is.</Data></Cell>
