<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Sociology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5946</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 175</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Creativity and Art</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Yaratıcılık kavramını tanır. Sanat dallarını sınıflandırır. Drama yöntemini öğrenir. Yaratıcı düşünme becerilerini geliştirir. Yaratıcı teknikleri kullanır. Sosyal ve mesleki yaşamda yaratıcı ve sanatsal faaliyetleri uygular. Yaratıcılığın önündeki engelleri değerlendirir.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=229927&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Sociology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5946</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 176</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Music, Individual and Society</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Recognize musical concepts. Learn about the periods of music history. Understand the relationship among the music, individual and society. Develop a sociological perspective on music. Use basic music knowledge in social life. Evaluate the relationship among the music, individual and society. Discusse music, a branch of art, with an interdisciplinary approach.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=229926&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
