<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5946</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 110</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Culture, Body and Gender Roles</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">What is the human body? What is the social dimension of the body? However, the body has become more than just a subject of medical interest and has become a subject of Human Sciences.</Data></Cell>
